## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project demonstrates how **software engineering principles**â€”specifically **multi-level Data Flow Diagrams (DFDs)** and **UML Class Diagrams**â€”are used to design a **robust, scalable, and user-friendly University Management System (UMS)**.

