## ğŸ”„ DFD + UML Integration

**DFDs** â†’ Focus on *how* data flows (dynamic aspect)  
**UML** â†’ Focus on *how* data is structured (static aspect)  

**Combined Benefit:**  
- Complete functional and structural blueprint  
- Prevents misalignment between business logic and system architecture  

